Václav Poživil himself is one of the recognized experts. For example, he participated in a unique operation in which the Ústí cheetah Jane was the first cheetah in the world to receive a total endoprosthesis. He served as director of the zoo from 2009 to 2012. He did not comment on anonymous slander against his person. Yesterday, he did not accept phone calls or respond to SMS text messages.
