The pair wrapped the bitch with tape and drowned her in the river, the children found the bag
The case took place at the end of July in the village around Valašské Klobouk. A 27-year-old woman brought home a one to two-year-old dog, which she wanted to take care of. However, her partner, who is ten years older, did not like the fact that it was a female dog, so he decided to get rid of it.
"He wrapped the animal with adhesive tape and rope and significantly eliminated its vocal expression. He put the dog in a jute bag, which he tied up. Then they took the animal together to the river, where they threw it in a bag. At the moment when the dog was thrown into the water, the dog was demonstrably alive," said Zlín police spokeswoman Monika Kozumplíková.
