2.1 Under the terms of this Agreement, for a fee, so that the Customer can properly use the Application, the Contractor will provide the Services to the Customer. The Contractor provides the Services for those parts of the Application that are listed in Appendix No. 3 (Description of Application Components and Documentation). The Contractor will make the best possible effort that can be reasonably required of him to provide the Services at the highest possible level.
