3.1 The Client shall pay the Contractor the Remuneration for the properly provided Services. The Remuneration shall include all costs incurred by the Contractor in connection with the provision of the Services. The Remuneration shall also include the costs of third party services used by the Contractor in the provision of the Services. The amount of the Remuneration shall be calculated in accordance with Annex No. 2 (Remuneration).
