The Client has the right to return the tax document before its due date. If the Client returns the tax document before its due date, the Client will inform the Contractor of the deficiencies for which the tax document was returned. After the delivery of a new or corrected tax document, a new due date begins.
4.6 If the Client does not pay the Remuneration by the due date, the Client shall pay the Contractor default interest for each day of delay in the amount of 0.05% of the amount with which the Client is in default. If the Client does not pay the Remuneration or part thereof due to a claim for defects in the Services, it is not in default.
