5.1 By signing this document, the Contractor declares that, as of the date of conclusion of this Agreement, it is not an unreliable payer within the meaning of Act No. 235/2004 Coll., on Value Added Tax (hereinafter referred to as "VAT"). If, during the term of this Agreement, the Contractor becomes an unreliable payer within the meaning of VAT, it shall immediately notify the Client of this fact.
