Annex 13 / Content of the contract for work
1. Capitalized terms / All words and phrases that begin with capital letters, the meaning of which is not determined by this work agreement (hereinafter referred to as the "Agreement"), have the same meaning as in the contract for the provision of services to support the operation and development of the information system - Service level agreement, the subject of which is the maintenance and development of the Application (hereinafter referred to as the "SLA").
2. Subject of the Agreement / Under the terms of this Agreement, for a fee, at his own expense and risk, the Contractor shall perform a work for the Client, the exact description of which is given in the Change Documentation (hereinafter referred to as the "Work").
3. The deadline for the execution of the Work / The Work shall be carried out by the Contractor by the deadline specified in the Change Documentation.
4. Price / For a properly completed Work, the Client shall pay the Contractor the Price specified in the Change Documentation (hereinafter referred to as the "Price").
5. Payment of the Price / Price The Client shall pay to the Contractor after acceptance of the Work, in accordance with the SLA.
6. Other costs for the production of the Work / The price includes all costs incurred by the Contractor in connection with the production of the Work. The price also includes expenses for the performance of third parties used by the Contractor in the production of the Work, in particular the costs for the performance of subcontractors, including authors and other external licensors, etc.
7. Interest on arrears / If the Client does not pay the Price by the due date, the Client shall pay the Contractor interest on arrears for each day of delay in the amount of 0.05% of the amount with which the Client is in arrears. If the Client does not pay the Price or part thereof due to a claim for defects in the Work, he is not in arrears.
8. Execution of the Work / Procedures in accordance with the SLA will be applied to the execution of the Work.
9. Acceptance Procedure / The place of delivery and acceptance of the Work is the Customer's registered office. The Acceptance Procedure will be used to accept the Work in accordance with the SLA.
10. Defects of the Work / The Work has a defect if it does not have the properties specified in this Agreement and the Change Documentation.
11. Obligation to exchange information / The Parties shall exchange all information necessary for the performance of this Agreement.
12. Instructions / If the Client issues a written instruction aimed at fulfilling the subject matter of this Agreement and if such instruction is not contrary to the legitimate interests of the Parties, the Contractor shall comply with such instruction. The Contractor shall notify the Client of the unsuitability of its instructions without undue delay after such unsuitable instruction is delivered to the Contractor. If it is not possible to issue the necessary instruction in time, the Contractor will act conscientiously at its own discretion and with knowledge of the Client's presumed interests.
13. Obligation to cooperate / In order to produce the Work, the Client shall provide the Contractor with all the cooperation that can reasonably be required of him. If the Client does not provide cooperation and as a result there is a delay in the production of the Work, the delivery period is extended by the period during which the Client did not provide cooperation.
14. Compliance of the Work with legal regulations / The Contractor shall prepare the Work in such a way that it complies with the generally binding legal regulations of the Czech Republic and this Agreement. The Work must not infringe any intellectual property right of a third party, nor patent protection, trademark, copyright or trade secret.
