Domestic banks partially corrected the declines of the past few days. Komerční banka improved by 0.82 percent to 803 crowns and Moneta Money Bank by 0.41 percent to 72.80 crowns. Avast shares appreciated by 0.89 percent to 113 crowns and the O2 operator gained 0.46 percent to 216.50 crowns.
