Strawberry, plum and invisible. Choose the right shade of lipstick: There is not just one red
When choosing a red lipstick, you should first determine whether you are a warm or cold type. Try a simple test - look at the veins on your wrist. If they are blue, you are a cold type, if they are green, then you are a warm type. When choosing a new red lipstick, first of all, put it on the distribution based on the undertone. Only in the next one, look at the texture.
If you are a woman with a cold undertone, then lipsticks in purple, plum, cherry or mauve are suitable for you.
If you fall into the category of warm skin undertone, choose such lipsticks. You can recognize them by the fact that they tend to have orange, coral, gold or brown reflections.
It may happen to you that some veins look green and others blue. In that case, congratulate yourself - you do not have to look at the undertone and you can focus only on your color preferences.
